    "body": "\"I expect that --snapshots=false completely disables the snapshots feature.\" - we don't support changing big node modes after startup - to reduce amount of unreproducible bugs - when user enabling/disabling/enabling/disabling things and then error happens. Unlikely we can test such cases. \r\n\r\nCurrently value of --snapshots flag stored in db at startup. \r\n\r\nSame about --prune flags. \r\n\r\n",
